commit 5e03ad6d87ce666bdef5be5f39584ff12bb6d341
Merge: 3f8e6c0 57db5f2
Author: Constantin Rack <c-rack@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Tue Dec 6 19:34:20 2016 +0100

    Merge pull request #2240 from bluca/aix_poll
    
